    <ul>
        <li>Web Applications: Java is widely used for building server-side applications using Java EE.</li>
        <li>Mobile Applications: Android development primarily uses Java (although Kotlin is also widely used now).</li>
        <li>Desktop GUI Applications: Applications using frameworks such as Swing and JavaFX.</li>
        <li>Enterprise Solutions: Large-scale applications using frameworks like Spring.</li>
    </ul>

